---
title: Pan-Roasted Chicken with Dijon Mushroom Sauce and Brown Rice
description: Dijon mustard - one of our favorite secret weapons in the kitchen - is the key to this hearty sauce. Though simple, this dish is packed with intense flavors like garlic and thyme to make this chicken dinner unique.
